# Restaurant Engine — environment template
#
# Copy to `.env` for local development. `.env` is gitignored and must never
# be committed. Every variable added here must use a safe placeholder value,
# never a real credential.
#
# Milestone 0 defines no runtime, so no variables are required yet.
# Milestone 1 introduces the first real variables (for example DATABASE_URL
# and APP_ENV); they will be added here in the same change that consumes them,
# per docs/05_DEVELOPMENT_WORKFLOW.md.
